steps.name: Given User should be on the Home web page
And User should be on the Main web page and signed as owner
Given deleted folder with some file and folder
log _> FOLDER: [cyA.Global Intranet Consultant] ~ created is Successful
assert expected **<div.tooltip.folder-tooltip>** to exist in the DOM
uncaught exception TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'constructor')
assert expected **<div.file__title.text--14.text--medium>** to exist in the DOM
log _> Delete ITEM by SLUG:b97988f2-c90a-424a-ac07-91f5c5a33dc8 ~ is Successful
And user must be in the "DELETED" section
When user clicks "Delete permanently" in the context menu of the target "Folder"
And user submits modal form "Delete permanently"
Then this "folder" has been permanently deleted
assert expected **{ message: success }** to have property **message** of **success**
And this "folder" does not displayed in the Deleted section
assert expected **[ <section.home__page>, 7 more... ]** not to contain **cyA.Global Intranet Consultant**
